rows.label: tev014501_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Keith about the status of NLA's infrastructure.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014501_MSG0001
rows.name:
We've finished building the Biahno water-purification
plant, but as far as this area itself goes, it's still as
dangerous as ever.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014501_MSG0002
rows.name:
A BLADE that was patrolling around here was attacked
and wounded by a weird indigen known as a cantor.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014501_MSG0003
rows.name:
We're actually thinking of posting another bounty
mission. So if you're willing to take it on,
I hope you wipe those things out for us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014501_MSG0008
rows.name:
Do you remember what I said before? About how we
could make great booze with this water?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014501_MSG0009
rows.name:
I mentioned that to Ajoa, and she told me to stop
talking and make it happen![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev014501_MSG0010
rows.name:
I guess we've got the water handled. Now we just
need to start planting some grain fields.[ST:wait ]
